{"tid":1310224,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"［急問］拎BNO去杜拜點樣整簽證","createTime":"2019-07-12T14:38:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T02:35:14.000Z","uid":278698,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b7475c5420a485f270399c6be24f36436b9bfe24","tid":1310224,"uid":278698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T14:38:16.000Z","msg":"小弟因爲揸BNO, 特衰護照又唔見左<br />\n下個月頭要去杜拜，本來以為BNO 可入免簽證入杜拜<br />\n點知原來要簽證，特衰唔見左，報失整過要等4-6個星期，一定趕唔切。<br />\n<br />\n因為唔見左特衰，冇得用正常領證程序，用5-10日就換到。<br />\n<br />\n我上網見過好到多e-visa 網，但唔知信唔信得過。<br />\n<br />\n比如下圖，去<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t6PxkUS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft6PxkUS.png&h=ce8d544b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去領事館整，之前爬文香港好似又冇得整。<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲試過整<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好人一生平安 <br />\n<br />\n感激不盡"},{"pid":"53272328662f807d1e50f1ec70ab2a5cf804c7cd","tid":1310224,"uid":278698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T14:39:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e314b65a1c5d51e54103d28aa9237c9040e0c6be","tid":1310224,"uid":1159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T14:50:08.000Z","msg":"搭EK"},{"pid":"b347876d0d8bface28986eb7e690d40c00016420","tid":1310224,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T14:56:50.000Z","msg":"所有e-visa都係假<br />\n最佳辦法係搭Emirates整埋"},{"pid":"063c38947f36fceb45e4ead9fb0c62c790aab16e","tid":1310224,"uid":278698,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b347876d0d8bface28986eb7e690d40c00016420","tid":1310224,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T14:56:50.000Z","msg":"所有e-visa都係假<br />\n最佳辦法係搭Emirates整埋"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T14:59:40.000Z","msg":"我跟團啊，可否聯絡旅行社搞機票果陣順便叫emirates 整埋"},{"pid":"06c33e1634ad6909802a6521dce36236b1